00:32:56,859 --> 00:32:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja je dobra,

778
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,240
[SPEAKER_00] ima za cilj promjenu.

779
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ima za cilj unutrašnju promjenu.

780
00:33:02,339 --> 00:33:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] A to je okretanje Bogu

781
00:33:03,579 --> 00:33:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] i okretanje čovjeku.

782
00:33:05,079 --> 00:33:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] Isto sakrament ispovjedi

783
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek vodi dalje.

784
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nije cilj sam sebi,

785
00:33:10,119 --> 00:33:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego vodi prema Euharistiji.

786
00:33:12,599 --> 00:33:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je Antun, rekao sam,

787
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] držao do Euharistije.

788
00:33:16,319 --> 00:33:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, samo bih ponovio ono

789
00:33:19,039 --> 00:33:20,339
[SPEAKER_00] što je Antun na svoj način

790
00:33:20,339 --> 00:33:22,740
[SPEAKER_00] jako važno naglašavao.

791
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:24,759
[SPEAKER_00] Važno je na koji se način

792
00:33:24,759 --> 00:33:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] pripremamo za ispovjed,

793
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] za sakramente Euharistije.

794
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] Na koji način primamo Euharistiju?

795
00:33:30,420 --> 00:33:31,660
[SPEAKER_00] A nekoliko puta.

796
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] I da zaključim,

797
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] par minuta je ostalo,

798
00:33:35,900 --> 00:33:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] čini mi se,

799
00:33:36,460 --> 00:33:39,700
[SPEAKER_00] svakako primjer svetog Antuna,

800
00:33:39,700 --> 00:33:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] velikog crkvenog naučitelja,

801
00:33:41,299 --> 00:33:43,339
[SPEAKER_00] može i treba biti putokazi

802
00:33:43,339 --> 00:33:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] u današnje vrijeme,

803
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] jer je sveti Antun znao

804
00:33:46,099 --> 00:33:47,319
[SPEAKER_00] biti toliko ponizan

805
00:33:47,319 --> 00:33:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] da ga nitko nije primijetio.

806
00:33:49,039 --> 00:33:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] Čistio je krumpio,

807
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] jer kaže se redno mjesto.

808
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:53,740
[SPEAKER_00] A znao je biti toliko učen

809
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] da su svi otvorili uši

810
00:33:55,759 --> 00:33:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] i slušali ono što on govori.

811
00:33:58,500 --> 00:34:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko skroman,

812
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] biti toliko skroman,

813
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:03,839
[SPEAKER_00] da te nitko ne primijećuje,

814
00:34:03,839 --> 00:34:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] a kad kažeš nešto,

815
00:34:06,799 --> 00:34:08,639
[SPEAKER_00] da se tvoja riječ čuje.

816
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je objedinjeno

817
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] u svetom Antunu.

818
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:14,139
[SPEAKER_00] To je fantastična Božja,

819
00:34:14,219 --> 00:34:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] veličina Božja proslava.

820
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže jedan istraživač

821
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] svetog Antuna,

822
00:34:20,639 --> 00:34:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] kaže ovako, citiram ga,

823
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] evanđelski naučitelj smatra

824
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] da krčanski život

825
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] nije nikako treniranje volje,

826
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] niti obično istraživanje

827
00:34:30,219 --> 00:34:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] abstraktnih istina.

828
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:33,639
[SPEAKER_00] Autentični krčanski život

829
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,840
[SPEAKER_00] je pronalaženje puta,

830
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] traženje čuvanje istine,

831
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] življenje života koji je Krist.

832
00:34:39,059 --> 00:34:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] Na samom kraju,

833
00:34:40,820 --> 00:34:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] da povežemo ono sa početkom,

834
00:34:43,019 --> 00:34:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] očito,

835
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] pametni intelektualac,

836
00:34:46,420 --> 00:34:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] sveti Antun,

837
00:34:47,340 --> 00:34:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] znao se tako lijepo spustiti

838
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] i postati uzor

839
00:34:51,559 --> 00:34:53,179
[SPEAKER_00] nama jednostavnim,

840
00:34:53,179 --> 00:34:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] običnim ljudima.

841
00:34:54,039 --> 00:34:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što je

842
00:34:55,820 --> 00:34:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] neintelektualac,

843
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] sveti Franjo Asiški,

844
00:34:58,780 --> 00:35:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] znao duševiti

845
00:35:00,260 --> 00:35:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] intelektualne slojeve društve.

846
00:35:02,420 --> 00:35:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ja kažem da

847
00:35:04,539 --> 00:35:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] i to govori

848
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] kako su naši ljudski parametri

849
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji put stvarno čudni,

850
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:11,400
[SPEAKER_00] da ne kažem krivi.

851
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko, evo i malo previše od mene.

852
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam na pozornosti.

853
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,840
[UNKNOWN] Hvala.

